\id TIT
\h Tito
\toc1 Kart daa bzej Páblona' na' bseḻeen lao Títona'
\toc2 Tito
\toc3 Tit.
\mt1 Kart daa bzej Páblona' na' bseḻeen lao Títona'
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 Nad' Pablo chzej' li', nak' wen llin c̱he Chioza' na' nak' postl c̱he Jesucrístona', na' bseḻee nad' kwenc̱he gaklen' beṉ'ka' ba wlej Chioza' gonḻilall'gake'ne' na' gombia'gake' daa nak dii ḻi daa chzajniin cho' goncho ka cheenile'.
\v 2 Na' zoacho noncho lez to yeḻ' mban zejḻi kaṉi. Kana' zi' wx̱e wsiltie' yell-lioni, Chios, beena' biga chziye', bc̱hebe' goṉe'n cho'.
\v 3 Na' ṉaa ba bllin lla, Chioza', beena' chisla cho' kwenc̱he bi kwiayi'cho, chzenile' yog' beṉ' cho'a xtilleena' daa bene' lall' na' chyix̱ji'a, kon ka wne' gon'.
\v 4 Chzej' li', Tito, nako' ka dowalj xiiṉ' daa nakcho toz chonḻilall'cho Jesucrístona'. X̱acho Chioza' na' Jesucrístona', beena' bisla cho' lao saaxya c̱hechoka' kwenc̱he bi kwiayi'cho, gaklenshgagake' li' na' gongake' ka so' mbalaz.
\p 
\v 5 Bkwaaṉa' li' Crétana' kwenc̱he wzeelo' koo xṉezi daa bi biyollicho, na'ch kwejo' beṉ' koo lo na'gake' beṉ'ka' nakgake' txen nonḻilall'gake' Crístona' to to yell, kon ka ba wnia' li' gono'.
\v 6 Beena' gak lall' nee beṉ'ka' nonḻilall' Crístona' chiyaḻ' wsa' c̱he' wen kwenc̱he bibi de iṉa beṉ' c̱he', na' gake' beṉ' zoa toz xoolin, na' gonḻilall' xiiṉe'ka' Crístona', na' bi gakgakb' bi' mal ni bi' widenag kwenc̱he bi wx̱a'gakb' cho'alao beṉ'.
\v 7 Daa ngoo lall' nee xshin Chioza', chiyaḻ' gake' dowalj beṉ' wen, beṉ' bibi de iṉa beṉ' c̱he', na' bi gake' beṉ' chep cha'lall', ni bi gake' beṉ' lok, ni weezo, ni wishagdiḻ, ni beṉ' wzelall'.
\v 8 San chiyaḻ' wi'e ga yigaaṉ beṉ', na' yibaile' gone' dii wen, na' gake' beṉ' nyeeṉ nyeeniyi, na' beṉ' nxi nyech, na' beṉ' chṉabia' kwinin.
\v 9 Chiyaḻ' gonlene' xtill' Chioza' daa nak dii ḻi daa ba nsede', kwenc̱he wtipe' lall' beṉ' yoblə daa wli' wsedile' ḻegake' daa nak dii ḻi, na' gone' ka shajḻe' beṉ'ka' nagake' aga kan' nakan.
\p 
\v 10 Ḻa' beṉ' zan inlleb beṉ' widenag zoa, beṉ' bizə chon chna, na' beṉ' chziye', na' zangake' nakgake' beṉ' Israel, beṉ'ka' na yog'ḻoḻte beṉ' byoka' chonḻilall'gake' Crístona' chiyaḻ' sho'gake' seṉ daa le circuncisión.
\v 11 Beṉ'kan' bi chiyaḻ' we'cho latj wli' wsedgakile' beṉ', ḻa' daa chzelall'gake' gongake' gan mechan' chdagake' to to yoo chli' chsedgakile' daa bi nak shḻi, na' chonllejgakile' do bxooṉtegake'.
\p 
\v 12 To beṉ' Creta, beṉ' chṉeyaa, wne' c̱he beṉ' wlall c̱he'ka': “Beṉ' Cretaki nakgake' beṉ' wxiye', beṉ' mal ga zeelo, beṉ' cheej chao ka nḻa' ka nte, na' beṉ' lia.”
\v 13 Na' dii ḻikzə ka nakannan'. Daan, bsheshlengake' ka chiyaḻi kwenc̱he shajni'gakile' daa nak dii ḻi daa ba wyajḻe'gake',
\v 14 na' bich wzenaggake' c̱he dill' golka' daa wdiljlall' beṉ' Israelka', ni bi wzenaggake' daa nazə beṉ'ka' chzoa ka'lə daa nak dii ḻi.
\p 
\v 15 Beṉ'ka' ba nxi nyech yic̱hjlall'do'eka' lao Chioza', ni daa cheej chaogake' ni daa chox̱'gake' bi chsej chllonan gak yic̱hjlall'do'eka' dii nxi nyech. San beṉ'ka' nxiṉj yic̱hjlall'do'eka' na' bi chajḻe'gake' c̱he Crístona', bibi dii nxi nyech de lawe'ka', ḻa' yic̱hjlall'do'eka'ten lle' lla' dii mala', na' ni bi chao chdian ḻegake' kat' chx̱iṉj chḻengake'.
\v 16 Nazgake' nombia'gake' Chioza', per diika' chongake' chili'n laogake' bi nombia'gake'ne'. Ḻa' nakgake' beṉ' mal ga wdelawin, na' nakgake' beṉ' bi chzoa dill', na' biga gakkzə gongake' daa nak dii wen.
\c 2
\p 
\v 1 Na' li' ṉaa, bli' bsedi beṉ' daa nak dii ḻi.
\v 2 Bzajnii beṉ' golka' gakgake' beṉ' nsa' c̱heyin wen, beṉ' chidoḻ' gap beṉ' ḻegake' balaaṉ, beṉ' nyeeṉ nyeeniyi, na' soac̱hec̱hgake' gonḻilall'gake' Crístona', na' gakgakile' beṉ', na' so sakgakile' bittez dii yen ile'gakile'.
\v 3 Ḻekzka' nool golka' chiyaḻ' gall illebgake' Chioza', na' bi gakzgake' beṉ' wic̱hitj dill', ni bi we'gake' latj gonzə yeḻ' weezona' ḻegake' gan, san chiyaḻ' gongake' wen kwenc̱he ile'i beṉ' ka chiyaḻ' gongake'.
\v 4 Na' wli' wsedgakile' nool xkwid'ka' gaki beṉ' c̱he'ka' na' gaki xiiṉe'ka',
\v 5 na' gakgake' beṉ' nyeeṉ nyeeniyi, beṉ' bi nda' nchen dii mal, na' gap wwia ḻoo yoo lillgake', gakgake' beṉ' chiyesh'lallii, na' wḻex̱j yic̱hjgake' lao beṉ' c̱he'ka' kwenc̱he kono iṉe zban c̱he xtill' Chioza' ni c̱hegake'.
\p 
\v 6 Na' ḻekzka' goll bi' wew'ka' gakgakb' bi' nyeeṉ nyeeniyi.
\v 7 Li'yeṉ'an chiyaḻ' wli'o chono' wen lao yog'ḻoḻte daa chono'. Na' wsa' c̱ho' bash bal kat' wli' wsedilo' beṉ' na' benan do yic̱hj do lalloo,
\v 8 na' wsako' wi'o dill' kwenc̱he bibi de iṉa beṉ' c̱heyin. Na' yido'i beṉ'ka' chakzbani cho' daa bibi de gon iṉagake' c̱hecho.
\p 
\v 9 Bzajnii beṉ'ka' yoo x̱anin wḻex̱j yic̱hjgake' lao x̱ane'ka', na' gongake' ka yiyoolall'gake', na' bi yilliizgake' ḻegake' dill'.
\v 10 Na' bibi si' kwangake' c̱he x̱ane'ka', san soa do lall'gake' kwenc̱he wli'gake' lao yog'ḻoḻ daa chongake' nan ḻe wen nak cho'a xtill' Chioza', beena' bisla cho' kwenc̱he bi kwiayi'cho.
\p 
\v 11 Chioza' ba bliile' yog'ḻoḻ beṉ' yeḻ' goklen c̱he'na' kwenc̱he yilagake' na' bi kwiayi'gake'.
\v 12 Na' yeḻ' goklenna' daa bene' c̱hecho chli' chsedin cho' kwej yic̱hjcho daa bi nak wen na' diika' chzelall' beli chenna', na' soacho yell-lioni nyeeṉ nyeeniyicho, goncho ka chiyoolall' Chioza', na' gall illebchone',
\v 13 shlak noncho lez illin lla choo lla xenna' yila' Jesucrístona', beena' nak beṉ' choo beṉ' xen, na' nake' Chios c̱hecho na' bisle' cho.
\v 14 Ḻen' bzani yeḻ' mban c̱he'na' ni c̱hecho kwenc̱he bisell biḻee cho' lao yog'ḻoḻ dii mala', na' bix̱is biyibe' cho' kwenc̱he gakcho lall' nee na' selall'cho goncho daa nak wen.
\p 
\v 15 Dgan chiyaḻ' wli' wsedilo' beṉ', na' wtipo' lall'gake' gongake' ka cheeni Chioza', na' wsheshleno' beṉ'ka' bi chon wen, na' benan ḻega beṉ' nzoa Chioza'. Na' kono chiyaḻ' gonzi li' nakzi.
\c 3
\p 
\v 1 Bisa'lall'gake' wḻex̱j yic̱hjgake' lao beṉ'ka' chṉabia', na' gakgake' beṉ' wizoa dill', na' segake' wṉeyi gongake' daa nak wen.
\v 2 Bibi gon iṉazgake' c̱he beṉ', san soalengake' beṉ' mbalaz na' gongakile' ḻegake' wen, na' gakgake' beṉ' gax̱jlall' lao yog'ḻoḻ beṉ'.
\p 
\v 3 Ḻekzka' cho', kana' gokcho beṉ' bi nteyi na' beṉ' bi bzoa dill', na' gosh' wlall'cho lao dii mala', na' btakw bc̱hej biya diika' bibayi beli chen c̱hechona' cho', na' gokcho beṉ' xe'. Gokzbani beṉ' cho' na' gokzbani ljwellcho ganga.
\v 4 Na' Chioza', beena' bisla cho' kwenc̱he bi kwiayi'cho, bliile' cho' yeḻ' beṉ' wen c̱he'na' len yeḻ' chaki c̱he'na'.
\v 5 Aga iṉacho daa bencho dii wennan' bisle' cho', san daa biyesh'lall'lile' cho'n. Na' bix̱is biyibe' yic̱hjlall'do'chona' kwenc̱he biyakcho beṉ' wen, na' Espíritu Santo c̱he'na' bikobe' yeḻ' mban c̱hechona'.
\v 6 Na' daa wit Jesucrístona', beena' bisla cho', Chioza' bzoe' Espíritu Santo c̱he'na' ḻoo yic̱hjlall'do'choki.
\v 7 Na' daa biyesh'lallile' cho', biyone' cho' beṉ' ḻi beṉ' shao' kwenc̱he goncho lez ikaacho yeḻ' mbanna' nak zejḻi kaṉi.
\p 
\v 8 Dillii nakan dii wx̱enlall'cho. Na' cheenid' gono' to dii byen wli' wsedilo'n beṉ'ka' chajḻe' c̱he Chioza' kwenc̱he segake' wṉeyi gongake' wen. Diikin nakgakan wen na' gaklenan yog' beṉ'.
\v 9 Bi gakguedlenzo' beṉ' ni c̱he cho'a dill'ka' chyiljlall'gake', ni daa nazgake' ben dii x̱ozxtoe'ka' daa bi chiyoll chido, ni bi gaklebilo' beṉ'ka' chakguedz ni c̱he leya' daa bzej dii Moiséza'. Ḻa' bi chaklengakan beṉ' na' bibi zak'gakan.
\p 
\v 10 Na' shi no chgoo beṉ'ka' dill' kwenc̱he gakgake' c̱hoplə, chiyaḻ' we'leno'ne' dill' bich gone' ka', na' shi ba gollo'ne' ka' to c̱hop shii na' bi chzenagkze', bkwaschokle' ka'lə.
\v 11 Ḻa' ṉezicho to kwinzen' chlliayi' kwine' daa nxiṉj yic̱hjlall'do'ena' na' chontie' dii mala'.
\p 
\v 12 Kat' wseḻaa Artémaza' wa Tíquicona' gana' zo', ben to dii byen yidwio' nad' yell Nicópoliza', ḻa' na' ba nc̱hoglallaa lljsoa' shlak te beo'ka' chbe' dii zaga'.
\v 13 Goklengach ga zeelo gako' Zénaza', beena' nsed ley c̱he Rómana', na'ch Apóloza'. Be'gake' daa chyallj chc̱hingakile' kwenc̱he koochgake' nez na' bibi iyalljgakile'.
\v 14 Na' ḻekzka' beṉ'ka' nakcho toz chiyaḻ' sho'logake' gongake' daa nak wen na' gaklengake' beṉ' shi bi chyallj chc̱hingakile' kwenc̱he ka' wgongake' llin daa ba nsedgake'.
\p 
\v 15 Yog'ḻoḻ beṉ'ki zoalen nad' ni chwapgake' li' chiox. Bwapgach chiox yog'ḻoḻ beṉ'ka' lle' na', beṉ'ka' chakgakile' cho' daa nakcho txen chonḻilall'cho Crístona'. Chioza' gaklenshgue' yog'ḻoḻ-le. Ka' gakan.
